<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="jn1036b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="jn1" href="#jn1036">JN1: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/jn1all.htm#jn1036b"> (NLI.2A) 36(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <p class="set">Helas! La Palice est mort <br>Il est mort devant Pavie <br>Helas! S&apos;il n&apos;&eacute;tait pas mort <br>Il ferait encore envie</p> <p class="set">Helas! La Palice est mort <br>Il est mort devant Pavie <br>Un quart d&apos;heure avant sa mort, <br>Il &eacute;tait encore en vie.</p> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Alas! La Palice has died / He died before Pavia / Alas! If he wasn&apos;t dead, / He would still be envied. <p>Alas! La Palice has died / He died before Pavia / A quarter of an hour before he died, / He was still alive.</p> <p class="spbr">Jacques de la Palice died in the battle of Pavia (1525), while fighting against the Spanish armies as a Marshal under Francis I. The epitaph on his tombstone reads: <i>Ci-g&icirc;t le Seigneur de La Palice: Si il&apos; n&apos;&eacute;tait pas mort, il ferait encore envie</i>.</p> </mm> </dd></dl>
